                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10138" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MGEC-0091</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">314 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">永德沃森的决策十字路口：扩张还是稳步前行</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yongde Watson&#39;s Decision-making Crossroad: Expansion or Steady Progress</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李亚玲，饶静，字礼春，熊道凤</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">熊道凤</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">永德沃森农业开发有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机会成本；规模经济；资源与能力；资本结构控制权；企业社会责任；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Opportunity cost; Economies of scale; Resources and capabilities; Capital structure control rights; corporate social responsibility</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着乡村振兴战略的持续推进，农业企业正面临从小规模、低密度的传统经营模式向品牌化、专业化、责任型企业的深度转型。本案例以永德沃森农业开发有限公司为例，系统梳理了一家乡村特色企业在资源有限、机会骤现背景下的战略抉择过程。面对一笔来自马来西亚的大额订单，企业创始人李小娟需要权衡扩张与维持原状之间的风险与回报，并对是否扩大产能、如何扩大产能进行抉择，其抉择不仅关乎企业自身，更与企业经营理念的守护和社会责任相关。案例总结了永德沃森在乡村振兴背景下的优势与劣势，以及外部环境的机会与威胁，并对“稳步前行”还是“扩张”两种路径的利弊进行比较分析，深入探讨企业如何在复杂环境中做出战略判断。本案例旨在帮助企业在扩张冲动与风险控制之间实现平衡，提升其在不确定环境下的战略判断力与树立长期主义视野；启发学员思考不同战略选择的利弊以及企业发展背后的初心与使命，理解企业商业决策的深层价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the continuous advancement of the rural revitalization strategy, 
agricultural enterprises are undergoing a profound transformation from the traditional business model of small scale and low density to brand-oriented, specialized and responsible enterprises.This case takes Yongde Watson Agricultural Development Co., Ltd. as an example to systematically sort out the strategic decision-making process of a rural characteristic enterprise under the background of limited resources and sudden emergence of opportunities.Facing a large order from Malaysia, Li Xiaojuan, the founder of the enterprise, needs to weigh the risks and returns between expansion and maintaining the status quo, and make a choice on whether to expand production capacity and how to do so. Her decision is not only related to the enterprise itself, but also related to the protection of enterprise business philosophy and social responsibility. The case summarizes the advantages and disadvantages of Yongde Watson in the context of rural revitalization, as well as the opportunities and threats in the external environment. It also conducts a comparative analysis of the  advantages and disadvantages of the two paths of &quot;steady progress&quot; or &quot;expansion&quot;, and deeply explores how enterprises can make strategic judgments in a complex environment.This case aims to help enterprises strike a balance between expansion impulse and risk control, enhance their strategic judgment in an uncertain environment and establish a long-term perspective. The case will inspire trainees to think about the advantages and disadvantages of different strategic choices as well as the original intention and mission behind the development of enterprises, and understand the profound value of business decisions of enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理经济学》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机会成本；规模报酬原理；资源基础观；资源与能力分析；资本结构控制权；企业社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
